- dictionary(domains*): DomainDictionary — assembles the cross-domain registry from defined domains.
- validate(domain): Seq[String] — rigor battery: self-declaration (domainAspect.typeName == typeName),
  completeness (no member is a stub), draco-internal derivation resolvability (every ancestor loads; external
